text: Federica Macrì (born 22 August 1990) is an Italian gymnast. She competed in three events at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Trieste
